## Changes Made

### Backend (Spring Security)
- [SecurityConfig.java](file:///c:/Users/swarn/OneDrive/Desktop/smart-resume-backend-final/src/main/java/com/smartresume/config/SecurityConfig.java): Implemented custom `JwtDecoderFactory` and Issuer Validator.
- [CustomOAuth2AuthorizationRequestResolver.java](file:///c:/Users/swarn/OneDrive/Desktop/smart-resume-backend-final/src/main/java/com/smartresume/config/CustomOAuth2AuthorizationRequestResolver.java): Explicitly stripped PKCE parameters.

### ML Service (Python)
- [ml_logic.py](file:///c:/Users/swarn/OneDrive/Desktop/smart-resume-backend-final/ml-service/ml_logic.py): Implemented Hash Set tokenization and optimized parsing loops.

